<figureCitation id="B6FB2A56FFADFFDFF39591DFFEB0CD42" box="[151,257,1514,1539]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1916,1938]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,195,1883]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,193,1895]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 4. Distribution of Hylaeus species in Mongolia: a — H. sibiricus, H. pirus; b — H. pfankuchi, H. gracilicornis; c — H. przewalskyi, H. paulus; d — H. tsingtauensis, H. nimbatus; e — H. stubbei, H. valinis; f — H. confusus, H. ulanus; g — H. dorni, H. montivagus; h — H. kozlovi sp. n.; i — H. mongolicus, H. potanini; j — H. mellon sp. n." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/256901/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="366">
